data.description: Pre-Inspected!!! Well maintained & beautifully decorated. Open & spacious w/ vaulted ceilings. Spectacular kitchen has granite, tile backsplash, pantry, eat-in area & open to living room w/ wood laminate flooring. 3 beds on the main. All appliances included. Master has walk-in closet & full bath. Family room in basement has window for natural light. Oversized garage. Large patio w/ firepit great for entertaining. Flat fenced yard & mature landscaping. Easy interstate access.
